{
  "id": "RAW_d9a18724",
  "title": "会用电脑还会持续进化：美团 EvoCUA，把 Agent 从“模仿”带进“经验时代”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODkzMzMwMQ==&mid=2650450801&idx=1&sn=6cb366a49c10e29b64031a49995e29fa",
  "date": "2026-01-23 11:51:00",
  "author": "AINLP",
  "siteName": "AINLP",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"background-color:inherit;font-size:17px;\">最近，美团联合复旦大学、同济大学、香港科技大学等团队，开源了新一代 Computer Use Agent 框架 ——</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:inherit;font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">EvoCUA</span><span style=\"background-color:inherit;font-size:17px;\">。这项工作不仅在 OSWorld 基准上刷新了开源模型的最好成绩，更重要的是，它系统性地提出了一条新的训练范式：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"376\" data-end=\"418\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不再只依赖静态数据模仿，而是让 Agent 通过可扩展的交互经验，实现持续自我进化。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"2\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在多模态 Agent 进入落地阶段的当下，这项工作，实际上给出了一个关键方向：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"3\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">如果想让 AI 像人一样熟练使用电脑，靠“喂数据”已经不够，必须让模型在真实环境中不断试错、总结和进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3788187372708758\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"982\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"502967152\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b57f2768&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJ7dIG6OlHaYvRRVv2X8vdrm9gqZVYpZoTrCjd3UGCVwTGgITyKm95aWe7HAASTLiaL3w3kk2pqP6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"cursor:pointer;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;list-style-type:disc;font-family:Optima, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, PingFangSC-regular, serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 25px;margin:8px 0px;letter-spacing:normal;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;cursor: pointer;\">\n    <p style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:5px 0px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkp3adac22jf\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border-radius:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;background:none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Github</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">: <a href=\"https://github.com/meituan/EvoCUA\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/meituan/EvoCUA</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;cursor: pointer;\">\n    <p style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:5px 0px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkp3adac1519\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border-radius:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;background:none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Huggingface</span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">：EvoCUA-32B、EvoCUA-8B</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;cursor: pointer;\">\n    <p style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:5px 0px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0em;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8em;box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-align:left;\"><strong mpa-font-style=\"mkp3adac6h1\" style=\"cursor:pointer;padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:15px;border-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);box-sizing:border-box;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);border-radius:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;background:none 0% 0% / auto no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);width:auto;border-width:3px;border-style:none;height:auto;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Technical Report</span></strong><span mpa-font-style=\"mkp3adac1v26\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">：</span><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/meituan/EvoCUA/blob/main/tech_report.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/meituan/EvoCUA/blob/main/tech_report.pdf</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"5\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">从“看别人操作”到“自己练出来”：CUA 的范式拐点</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"6\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">过去一年，Computer Use Agent 成为多模态领域的核心赛道。Claude、UI-TARS、OpenCUA 等系统已经展示出，让模型通过截图、鼠标、键盘来完成复杂 GUI 操作是可行的。但这些方法，大多建立在一个共同前提之上：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"8\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">👉<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">用大规模静态轨迹数据做模仿学习。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"9\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种方式在早期非常有效，但随着任务复杂度提升，很快就会遇到几个现实瓶颈：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"10\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">静态数据难以覆盖真实环境的状态空间</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"11\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">很多 GUI 任务具有强因果依赖，离线轨迹难以反映</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"12\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">长尾异常场景几乎无法人工构造</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"13\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型很难真正从失败中系统性学习</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"14\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EvoCUA 的核心判断是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">CUA 的 Scaling Law，应该从“数据规模”，转向“经验规模（experience scaling）”。</span>也就是说，让 Agent 像人一样：在真实环境中反复操作、试错、总结，从经验中进化能力。</span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"19\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">三大核心模块，构成 EvoCUA 的“自进化系统”</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"20\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文给 EvoCUA 设计了一套完整的闭环系统，而不是单点算法创新。整体可以拆成三个关键支柱：</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"21\" style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;\"><span leaf=\"\">1️⃣ 可验证任务合成引擎（Verifiable Synthesis Engine）</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"22\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 EvoCUA 的基础设施级创新。传统 synthetic data 最大的问题是：生成了任务，但很难严格验证是否真的完成。EvoCUA 引入的是「<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Generation-as-Validation</span>」范式：不仅生成指令（g）同时生成可执行验证器（Vg），在真实 sandbox 中执行验证。也就是说，每个任务天然带有<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">可执行的判定逻辑</span>，避免了自然语言 reward 的歧义和幻觉。在工程上，这个模块包括：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"31\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">分层 GUI 任务空间建模（浏览器、Office、终端等）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"32\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原子能力拆解（排序、公式、编辑、下载、搜索等）</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"33\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参数化 + 非参数化资源注入</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"34\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">真实环境中的闭环代码验证</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"35\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三重去污染（语义、配置、验证器）</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"36\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这使得 EvoCUA 能够规模化合成<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">严格可验证的高质量交互任务</span>，打破人工标注瓶颈。</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"38\" style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;\"><span leaf=\"\">2️⃣ 并发交互基础设施（Scalable Interaction Infrastructure）</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"39\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果说第一个模块解决了“任务从哪来”，第二个模块解决的是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">经验怎么规模化收集。</span>EvoCUA 构建了一套工业级的沙盒集群系统：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"42\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">QEMU-KVM + Docker 混合虚拟化</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"43\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">异步网关 + 分布式调度</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"44\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">单分钟内启动上万沙盒</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"45\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持 10 万级并发交互</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"46\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键不仅是吞吐量，而是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">高保真 GUI 环境</span>：输入映射确定性（避免键盘错位），字体注入保证渲染一致，网络与运行时稳定性修补，GUI 布局一致性。这让模型获得的经验，更接近真实用户的操作环境，而不是理想化模拟器。</span></p>\n  <h2 data-layout-id=\"53\" style=\"font-size: 17px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;\"><span leaf=\"\">3️⃣ 从经验中进化：不是一次训练，而是持续循环</span></h2>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"54\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EvoCUA 最核心的不是某个 RL 算法，而是一套<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">进化式学习流程</span>：冷启动（Cold Start）。用高质量合成交互轨迹，建立：统一 action space，结构化 thought space（显式推理），稳定的执行与终止模式，成功经验强化（RFT）。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"54\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过拒绝采样，筛选成功轨迹：动态分配 rollout 预算，集中计算资源在“边界任务”，去冗余、去噪，提炼高价值经验，从失败中学习（Step-level DPO）</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"66\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不是简单 trajectory 级 RL，而是：精确定位关键错误步骤，构造 step-level 偏好对，强化“纠错 + 反思 + 恢复”能力。最终形成一个循环：</span></p>\n  <blockquote style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:15px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\">\n   <p data-start=\"2180\" data-end=\"2217\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">合成任务 → 大规模交互 → 强化成功 → 修正失败 → 能力边界不断扩展</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"72\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这正是 EvoCUA 所说的：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"73\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">evolving paradigm via learning from experience</span></span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"75\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">实验结果：开源模型新 SOTA，不止靠大模型</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"76\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 OSWorld-Verified 基准上：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"77\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EvoCUA-32B：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">56.7%</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"78\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenCUA-72B：45.0%</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"79\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">UI-TARS-2（闭源）：53.1%</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"80\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">也就是说：用更小的开源模型，通过经验进化训练，超越更大的静态训练模型，甚至超过部分闭源系统，更有意思的是，小模型也显著受益：EvoCUA-8B：46.1%，超过 OpenCUA-72B（72B 参数），这说明：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"89\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">方法论比单纯扩大模型规模更重要。</span></span></p>\n  <h1 data-layout-id=\"91\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: 400;color: rgba(43, 119, 191, 1);margin-bottom: 12px;line-height: 2.0;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">行业意义：Agent 的 Scaling Law 正在改变</span></span></h1>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"92\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这项工作的真正价值，不在于一条 leaderboard，而在于给 Agent 训练提供了一条更可持续的路径：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"93\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从离线模仿 → 在线经验</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"94\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从数据扩容 → 经验扩容</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"95\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从轨迹学习 → 因果交互学习</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"96\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从静态能力 → 持续进化能力</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"97\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于真正要落地到复杂桌面环境、企业流程、自动化系统的 Agent 来说，这种范式，可能才是走向可靠性的关键。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"100\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">EvoCUA 不是一次局部改进，而是一次训练范式层面的升级：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"101\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把合成数据变成可验证任务</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"102\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把基础设施变成经验工厂</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-layout-id=\"103\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把训练流程变成自进化闭环</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"104\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从这个角度看，它真正解决的不是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“Agent 会不会用电脑”</span>，</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"106\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而是：</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"107\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“Agent 能不能像人一样，通过经验不断变强”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"108\" style=\"font-weight:300;font-size:17px;line-height:2.0;margin-bottom:24px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这，可能才是 Computer Use Agent 走向实用的关键一步。</span></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"59\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:300;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2074\" data-pm-sl