fileid=\"502967146\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=14411a67&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJ7dIG6OlHaYvRRVv2X8vdricGQEfUTPGJGgiakEMujl2u3Keo5xrw7cntYrFRQwSQRrpqib7FIibcJZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"502967147\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=333280c2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJ7dIG6OlHaYvRRVv2X8vdrElscZicuUl3bnyDic6iaf1yO5v6XMQicIzYwAJDfKG2lK7co0erQic97dKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"502967148\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1abc5df3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJ7dIG6OlHaYvRRVv2X8vdrCbwWWpHNE4iaFrt3aXEc5KMjGMsz401H7ibd7c5ATzxgGj7f7X0ZEPQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.2935185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"502967149\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=38b4507c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FnW2ZPfuYqSJ7dIG6OlHaYvRRVv2X8vdrTu2V2iby8iay5tdrbrB0ibrvEVss9wXibPic0geSAicDPIicIzMjlUSojOPww%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-layout-id=\"59\" data-pm-slice=\"4 1 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:300;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><strong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2074\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">感兴趣的朋友可以关注AINLP公众号回复'EvoCUA'获取该技术报告英中对照版pdf全文</span></span></strong></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "美团联合多所高校发布 EvoCUA 框架，通过“经验进化”范式取代传统“静态模仿”，在 OSWorld 基准上刷新开源模型纪录。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "美团联合多所高校发布 EvoCUA 框架，通过“经验进化”范式取代传统“静态模仿”，在 OSWorld 基准上刷新开源模型纪录。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了美团与复旦、同济、港科大等团队合作研发的 Computer Use Agent (CUA) 框架——EvoCUA。该框架针对传统 Agent 依赖静态数据模仿导致的泛化性差、无法处理长尾异常等问题，提出了“经验规模（Experience Scaling）”的新范式。EvoCUA 包含三大支柱：可验证任务合成引擎、支持 10 万级并发的工业级沙盒基础设施，以及基于强化学习的持续进化流程。实验显示，EvoCUA-32B 在 OSWorld-Verified 基准上达到 56.7%，超越了参数量更大的 OpenCUA-72B 及部分闭源模型，证明了通过真实环境试错与总结实现自我进化的有效性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "CUA 的 Scaling Law 正在从数据规模转向经验规模。",
      "explanation": "单纯增加静态模仿数据已遇到瓶颈，让 Agent 在真实环境中反复操作、试错并总结经验，是提升复杂 GUI 任务处理能力的关键。"
    },
    {
      "point": "引入「Generation-as-Validation」范式解决合成数据验证难题。",
      "explanation": "通过同时生成指令和可执行验证器，在沙盒中闭环验证任务完成情况，避免了自然语言奖励带来的歧义和幻觉。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建工业级并发交互基础设施是实现经验进化的前提。",
      "explanation": "利用虚拟化技术实现单分钟启动上万沙盒及 10 万级并发交互，确保模型能在大规模、高保真的真实环境中获取操作经验。"
    },
    {
